<br>
If I do use a regular pet I am usually the only one (I tend to do smallish raids) and let everyone know that I have hotkeyed my earthen boots and will use them if anyone so much as implies my pet is causing a problem or otherwise behaving weird.<br>
<br>
Pets are disposable in my book, no matter how buffed. /pet sit down is also a requirement, but even then sometimes they go wacky and it only takes one glance away from the monitor in a 6+hour raid to cause a TPW and much (deserved) hassle from the other raiders.<br>
<br>
56 mag.<br>
